issue.title: Error using playback of cloudsim log

content.raw:
could you try running the command below to download the subt\_tunnel\_staging\_area in your docker container?

```
ign fuel download --url "https://fuel.ignitionrobotics.org/openrobotics/models/subt_tunnel_staging_area/3" -v 4
```

Note that it specifically indicates it wants version 3 of the model. You may see a warning msg but it’s should be safe to ignore.

‌
